FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,FCouncillor Perry is expected to say:
OL,7,F"Balloons, including those marketed as
OL,8,Fbiodegradable, can remain in the
OL,9,Fenvironment for up to four years,
OL,10,Fcontributing to long-term litter and
OL,11,Fenvironmental contamination.
OL,13,F"National beach-clean monitoring has
OL,14,Fconsistently identified an average of
OL,15,Fthree balloons per 100 metres of
OL,16,Fcoastline during surveys, illustrating
OL,17,Fthe scale of the pollution issue.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,F"Wildlife, farm animals and marine
OL,7,Fspecies are at risk of injury,
OL,8,Fentanglement, starvation, or death
OL,9,Fthrough ingestion or entrapment in
OL,10,Fballoon debris, ribbons, and sky
OL,11,Flantern components ` including
OL,12,Fdocumented examples such as a juvenile
OL,13,Fgreen turtle found near Blackpool with
OL,14,Fballoon waste obstructing its
OL,15,Fdigestive tract.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,F"Evidence provided to the Civil
OL,7,FAviation Authority has identified
OL,8,Fincidents involving sky lanterns and
OL,9,Fhelium balloons interfering with
OL,10,Faviation operations, including
OL,11,Freported risks of ingestion into
OL,12,Faircraft engines, obstruction to
OL,13,Faircraft manoeuvring on the ground,
OL,14,Fand disruption or delay to take-off
OL,15,Fand landing.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,F"Sky lanterns pose serious fire risks,
OL,7,Fparticularly in rural and agricultural
OL,8,Fareas, with documented incidents
OL,9,Finvolving damage to crops, farm
OL,10,Fbuildings, stored feed, and harm to
OL,11,Flivestock."
OL,13,FMs Perry will also express how
OL,14,Fnational organisations - including the
OL,15,FMarine Conservation Society, NFU,
OL,16,FRSPCA, and RSPB - support bans on sky
OL,17,Flantern and balloon releases in the
OL,18,Finterests of environmental protection
OL,19,Fand animal welfare.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,FShe is expected to add how fire and
OL,7,Frescue bodies have "raised serious
OL,8,Fconcerns" about the risk associated
OL,9,Fwith sky lanterns and have called for
OL,10,Fan urgent review of their continued
OL,11,Fuse.
OL,13,FShe will add: "Cumberland's geography,
OL,14,Fincluding extensive agricultural land,
OL,15,Fdesignated ecological sites, and
OL,16,Fsensitive coastal and upland habitats,
OL,17,Fmakes this area particularly
OL,18,Fvulnerable to environmental damage,
OL,19,Fanimal welfare impacts and wildfire
OL,20,Frisk from sky lantern and balloon
OL,21,Freleases.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
