PN,35707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1778526672
OL,3,CBan on release of sky lanterns and
OL,4,Cballoons proposed to protect wildlife
OL,6,FSeveral local authorities have
OL,7,Fintroduced regulations on sky lantern
OL,8,Fand balloon releases within leases,
OL,9,Flicences, and event conditions
OL,10,Fsupported by proportionate public-
OL,11,Fawareness activity.
OL,13,FA growing number of local authorities,
OL,14,Fincluding Somerset West & Taunton,
OL,15,FShropshire, Melton, and South Ribble
OL,16,Fhave introduced bans.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
